”This is not the end; it is not even the beginning of the end
but perhaps, the end of the beginning 
For my mum - my best friend and role model
Anita Shaw 1948 2008"®
”In loving, everlasting memory of
Eden Harman Bernardy
"Love each other. Be kind to each other. Respect each other
And whenever you can, as much as you can,
LAUGH, DANCE, SING, & CELEBRATE LIFE"
Eden. your spirit lives within and around us. We love you
Beyond measure. Beyond words. ALWAYS"¬
¦In fond memory of
Our Founder Mrs June Mackay
Our Chairman John Perry
and Secretary Mrs Louise Perry (nee Conner)
from the members of the Brixton Dog Training Club"Ł
¬Peter Paul Zammit
7th May 1922-10th May 2012
A wonderful dad, grandad & great grandad. In memory of all
the happy times spent here in this park with your grandchildren"»
